template.value: <!-- Table $TABLE_NAME$ --> <changeSet id="$TABLE_NAME$_insert_on" author="Pavel Shabalin" runAlways="true" context="test"> <preConditions onFail="CONTINUE"> <dbms type="mssql"/> </preConditions> <sql>SET identity_insert $TABLE_NAME$ ON;</sql> <rollback/> </changeSet> <changeSet id="$TABLE_NAME$_data" author="Pavel Shabalin" runAlways="true" context="test"> <sql> $SQL$ </sql> <rollback/> </changeSet> <changeSet id="$TABLE_NAME$_id_seq_postgres" author="Pavel Shabalin" runAlways="true" context="test"> <preConditions onFail="CONTINUE"> <dbms type="postgresql"/> </preConditions> <sql>ALTER SEQUENCE $TABLE_NAME$_id_seq RESTART WITH $SEQ_RESTART$;</sql> <rollback/> </changeSet> <changeSet id="$TABLE_NAME$_insert_off" author="Pavel Shabalin" runAlways="true" context="test"> <preConditions onFail="CONTINUE"> <dbms type="mssql"/> </preConditions> <sql>SET identity_insert $TABLE_NAME$ OFF;</sql> <rollback/> </changeSet>
